1. The vector store implementation can initialize the requisite schema for you, but you must opt-in by specifying the <code>initializeSchema</code> boolean in the appropriate constructor or by setting <code>&#8230;&#8203;initialize-schema=true</code> in the <code>application.properties</code> file.
